{"tid":1831750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾南山更透露，甚至有1名病人感染14名醫護人員染病","createTime":"2020-01-20T15:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T15:46:40.000Z","uid":240448,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9c1ab32ebd65bc599553862371b449ecedaa3403","tid":1831750,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:26:28.000Z","msg":"最新消息<br />\nFrom Apple news"},{"pid":"4ec7395f40900691d301c1db50b7802b67422bdb","tid":1831750,"uid":240448,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:28:08.000Z","msg":"【新增內容】新型冠狀病毒引發的肺炎，來勢洶洶，全國確診個案最少有218宗。央視晚上報道，國家呼吸系統疾病臨床醫學研究中心主任鍾南山表示，<em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">根據目前的資料，新型冠狀病毒肺炎是肯定有人傳人，因為在廣東有2宗病例，均沒去過武漢，其家人去過武漢後，他們便染上新型冠狀病毒肺炎。此外，鍾南山更透露，甚至有1名病人感染14名醫護人員染病。</span></span></em>"},{"pid":"d85f9430cb61c8633686e656f67c2f1a6c6396ad","tid":1831750,"uid":33437,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:28:16.000Z","msg":"沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f1428cd4f832163dd81c2a75e0833ee59e7ed7","tid":1831750,"uid":240448,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:28:38.000Z","msg":"鐘南山指出，95%以上病例都跟武漢有關係，當中包括去過武漢，來自武漢的人；第二個特點是目前在廣東、武漢均有人傳人；第三個特點是有醫務人員被感染，有1名患者導致14個醫護人員感染。"},{"pid":"b309f6e3e08ad281f1749573fc15e96eb4ffdc67","tid":1831750,"uid":210727,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:28:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5160642f25dd1a6eb141ed3fb35ed54b08815ef8","tid":1831750,"uid":59518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:28:55.000Z","msg":"央視<br />\n話人傳人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"953188438962962363cf77ddb0a2e822c93eda57","tid":1831750,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家保護好自己丫"},{"pid":"5b5561e3557a333dc6e4ce8c11e5e49cb1641775","tid":1831750,"uid":240448,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:29:49.000Z","msg":"有本港專家表示，內地很注重體面，至今認為自己「攪得掂」，故未有邀請世衞專家到武漢視察；而當年2003年沙士，內地隱瞞疫情但卻未能控制疫情，甚至影響全球，才迫於與世衞合作，容許世衞專家到內地視察。<br />\n<br />\n鍾南山最為港人熟悉的，是他於2003年廣東爆發沙士時，否定了當時國家疾控中心關於「典型衣原體是非典型肺炎病因」的觀點，他為廣東衞生行政部門制訂救治方案，大大提高廣東地區沙士危重病人的成功搶救率。"},{"pid":"531ed195e7fc83842c107702da3efa9a68aa600b","tid":1831750,"uid":83558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:30:31.000Z","msg":"有黨無問題<br />\n口罩如垃圾"},{"pid":"f11897ab7509b1bc83983f56b42c042d4a24b9a6","tid":1831750,"uid":42521,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:31:24.000Z","msg":"咩叫有限度人傳人?"},{"pid":"79a0bbe131be5b632abbf4df9e67fee89e0fd1c0","tid":1831750,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:32:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2DVgtkj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2DVgtkj.png&h=d5b93d5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200120&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60503738\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200120%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60503738&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV951QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=ccda0924\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200120%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60503738&h=c2d559d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.